overview.longBusinessSummary: Dole plc engages in sourcing, processing, marketing, and distribution of fresh fruit and vegetables worldwide. It operates through three segments: Fresh Fruit; Diversified Fresh Produce - EMEA; and Diversified Fresh Produce - Americas and ROW. The company offers bananas, pineapples, grapes, berries, avocados, organic produce, cherries, kiwis, apples, cherries potato, and onion. The company offers its products under DOLE brand. It serves retailers, wholesalers, and foodservice customers. Dole plc was incorporated in 2017 and is headquartered in Dublin, Ireland.
